The Duchess of Sussex and Prince Harry’s wife, Meghan Markle
will soon be launching a fashion collection. According to royal report Omid Scobie, Meghan in the
upcoming September British Vogue issue spoke about her new partnership with
Smartworks. Smartworks is a charity that supports unemployed and defenceless women
re-entering the workplace.  Since Meghan Markle started dating Prince Harry, she become
a great influencer in the fashion world with her classy, simple and
